lead_paragraph: Germany said on Tuesday Sunday's final game of the Euro 2016 soccer championship in Paris could prove an attractive target for Islamic State, especially if hosts France, victim of November attacks, are playing.

headline.print_headline: Euro 2016 Final Attack Risk Grows With French Involvement-Germany
